title: Burn
body:
I propose Solar Moon development team adds a burn feature to

voting procedures
(20% of voting fee),

Sell feature
(20% selling fee BSC)
(20% reflections polygon),

Buy feature
(2% of purchase)

To decrease supply gradually over time,

Increasing value on demand.

Tokenomics
